7
00:01:38,299 --> 00:01:38,819
[SPEAKER_01] Da, wow.

8
00:01:38,819 --> 00:01:44,540
[SPEAKER_00] Po treći puta, i kao tako je rekorderka.

9
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:45,799
