10
00:01:45,799 --> 00:01:46,560
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi.

11
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi.

12
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:48,280
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala.

13
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:53,359
[SPEAKER_00] I svaki put, rado, razgovoram s tobom.

14
00:01:53,359 --> 00:02:01,920
[SPEAKER_00] Na početku, kad smo snimali prvi podcast, tvoj video je dosta dugo bio u top 3 najgledanija videa.

15
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:05,079
