16
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] Drugi video koji smo snimili, ja bih rekao da je još uvijek u top 10 nekako.

17
00:02:11,259 --> 00:02:13,580
[SPEAKER_00] Jedan i drugi su dosta visoko.

18
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:19,020
[SPEAKER_00] U zadnje vrijeme lud podcast dosta dobro raste.

19
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:22,060
[SPEAKER_00] I sretan sam i ponosan sam radi toga.

20
00:02:22,060 --> 00:02:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] Čestitam.

21
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:26,520
[SPEAKER_00] Sad smo na 5000 novih pratitelja svaki mjesec.

22
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,219
[SPEAKER_00] Najs.

23
00:02:27,219 --> 00:02:30,819
